Install
=======


Linux, Mac, or Windows
----------------------

   1. Extract the package to your local computer into a directory;

   2. At a terminal go to the directory where the package was extracted;

   In Linux or Mac:
   3. Verifies if the wap script is executable. If it not, then execute "chmod u+x wap" at the prompt;

   4. Run the script wap to use the tool. See in README file how you can use the tool.

   In Windows
   3. Run the batch file wap.bat to use the tool. See in README file how you can use the tool.


